snippet.title: Earthfall: Alien Horde Coming to Nintendo Switch!
snippet.description: Earthfall: Alien Horde is coming to Nintendo Switch on October 11th, and will include all previous content updates along with 4-player local co-op wireless play! #KillAllAliens http://bit.ly/2khLVlG
